dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. "500864 10-72." Maps  shows Armistice line, 1949, international and governorate boundaries, governorate capitals, three classes of roads, railroads, ports, and airfields. Shows roads, railways, national and governorate capitals, international and governorate boundaries, and armistice line of 1949. Includes location map, comparative size diagram, and ancillary maps showing population, land use, and economic activity.
